Moreover, some of the catastrophic events can also occur by human acts like Nuclear Weapons, Bio weapons, Nano tech Weapons, Fuel Shortage, Economic Collapse. Although politicians have long been aware of threats, the governments need to struggle to cope if disaster strikes.
           <br/>
           <br/>
           The aim of the scientists is to produce a doomsday list of threats which help them determine that what actually are more likely to occur, and to come up with a plan to defend the world against them with the hope of saving the humanity. There are many ways in which you can easily explain the work and the planning of developing a doomsday list. As you need to attend lots of conferences and seminars, your presentation may lack the attraction that is generally required to increase the interest of the viewers. Moreover, without a good presentation it will be hard to explain the observation, calculation and the estimation clearly. The best way is to increase the effectiveness of your presentation is to make an approach for the PowerPoint templates.

Exclusive stunning templates will also provide you enough space to easily consider other risks such as ecological disasters caused by climate change, and food shortages and pandemics that are getting fuelled by the rapidly growing world population.
           <br/>
           <br/>
           With an incredible collection of PowerPoint presentation templates you can easily explain the scientists' belief and the three major catastrophic events that can occur although there is a low probability:
           <br/>
